Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:59.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「君が許さなかった世界はこんなにも綺麗だ」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:05.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「悲しみを生むこと、全てが悪だとでも言うのか？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現実の銃口　突きつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}矜持たちが　壊れても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}僕は僕でしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:21.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Against the gunpoint, ready to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.81,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I'll rise like the break dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:26.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I save them for the final day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:29.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dream of the world for me and "fantasia"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:32.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It's time to go...Unshaken mind!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:42.70,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}揺れる視界を薙ぎ払い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愛すべき"正義"を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:53.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}語られない明日のために生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儚さと　痛みの中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}狂気だけが走らせる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全てが還る日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:07.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I face out, hold out to world!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:59.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「你所不原谅的世界是这样美丽」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:05.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「制造悲伤的一切都是邪恶吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.96,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现实的枪口已指向了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使矜持悉数破碎崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也仍然只是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:21.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迎着枪口 随时准备战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会像破晓的黎明那样喷薄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:26.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我为末日将他们拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:29.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向往着为我与幻想而存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:32.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是时候启程了…怀着坚定的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:42.70,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去改变世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}清空动摇的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寻找值得热爱的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:53.42,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为无从诉说的明天而生存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在虚幻与痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.55,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有疯狂在穿梭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在一切回归之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:07.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我将勇敢地面对世界
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:41.03,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}理想なんて幻想って時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:50.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}貴方は何処へ手を伸ばすの…たった一人で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:57.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}Always...All ways...You stand by Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:05.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}何を護るために苦しんでいるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:11.98,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}捕われてるままじゃ抱きしめられない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.06,0:23:19.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}標識の無い道で泣いているChild
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:27.16,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}理想なんて玩具だって知って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.49,0:23:35.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}それでも…その手を差し伸ばしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:42.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}きっと正義の見方なんて手の先の視線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:54.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}構わないよ、見ていたいだけ…たった一人を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:41.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}在这理想不过是幻想的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:50.83,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}你要孤身一人 将手伸向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:57.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}你永远 由始至终 都与正义为邻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:05.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}你是为了保护什么而如此痛苦?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:11.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}身陷囹圄就无法拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.06,0:23:19.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}孩子 在没有道标的路上哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:27.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}即便知道理想只是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.49,0:23:35.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}也仍然伸出手去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:42.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}对正义的见解一定只取决于视线的走向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:54.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}那样也无所谓 我只想要看着那唯一的人
